{"tid":847100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國9月私人職位勁升23萬個　就業市場持續強勁","createTime":"2018-10-04T02:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:28:30.000Z","uid":62257,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6c633c6956548a1b816ab60a80a9ebc0a64217","tid":847100,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181003/mobile/bkn-20181003201535801-1003_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181003%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181003201535801-1003_00842_001.html&d=%2FYputimRECP4bxIM%2BUTwT0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=489fa854\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181003/mobile/bkn-20181003201535801-1003_00842_001.html</a><br />\n數據機構ADP公布，美國9月份私人職位勁升23萬個，分別高過8月及市場預期的16.8萬及18.4萬個，反映當地就業市場持續強勁。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421183-20181003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421183-20181003.htm&d=%2FYputimRECP4bxIM%2BUTwT0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=999c8e0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421183-20181003.htm&h=12155c37\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421183-20181003.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國人力資源服務公司ADP公布，9月私人企業新增職位有23萬個，多過市場預期的18.5萬個，創2月以來最高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20181003203733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20181003203733&d=%2FYputimRECP4bxIM%2BUTwT0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a6e43a44\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20181003203733</a><br />\n美國就業服務機構ADP公布, 9月私人機構就業職位增加23萬個, 多過市場預期的18萬5000個, 增幅是2月以來最高.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8月增幅由原先公布的16萬3000個, 向上修正至16萬8000個."},{"pid":"e6